Package com.github.jessemull.microflexinteger.plate

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Plate
    This class represents a microplate used by chemists, biologists, physicists and many other natural science researchers.
    Stack
    Scientists commonly refer to a collection of microplates as a stack.
    Well
    This class represents a well in a microplate.
    WellIndex
    A wrapper for a row and column index pair.
    WellList
    Internal data structure to hold lists of well indices for well sets or plates.
    WellPrecursor<T extends java.lang.Number>
    This class represents a well in a microplate.
    WellSet
    This class represents a set of wells.
